OL,3,CCompostable packaging put to the test
OL,4,Cas cups take years to break down
OL,6,FA University of Portsmouth experiment
OL,7,Fis underway to test how long
OL,8,Fcompostable packaging takes to break
OL,9,Fdown, as ITV Meridian's Lucy Warhurst
OL,10,Ffound out.
OL,12,FAs the world tries to cut down on
OL,13,Fsingle-use plastics, compostable
OL,14,Fpackaging has emerged as a more
OL,15,Fsustainable solution.JWhat many of us
OL,16,Fdon't know is how best to compost it,
OL,17,Fand how long some will take to break
OL,18,Fdown.JScientists at the University of
OL,19,FPortsmouth are trying to find the
OL,20,Fanswers with a year-long experiment in
OL,21,FPetersfield.
