OL,6,FPHD Researcher, Anita Carey says:
OL,7,F"Compostable packaging has been
OL,8,Fdeveloped to replace single-use
OL,9,Fplastic, so the idea is that rather
OL,10,Fthan use your single-use plastic and
OL,11,Fput it in the bin, compostable
OL,12,Fpackaging can be put into your
OL,13,Fcomposting system and break down."
