OL,3,CCompostable packaging put to the test
OL,4,Cas cups take years to break down
OL,6,FAnita says many products don't say
OL,7,Fwhether they're suitable for home or
OL,8,Fcommercial systems, they don't all
OL,9,Finclude instructions and don't always
OL,10,Fwork as well as people might expect.
OL,11,FAnita adds: "What people are reporting
OL,12,Fis that when they go to take the
OL,13,Fcompost out of their composting
OL,14,Fsystem, the compost is ready but
OL,15,Fthey're still finding pieces of
OL,16,Fcompostable packaging."
