OL,3,CCompostable packaging put to the test
OL,4,Cas cups take years to break down
OL,6,FJoanne Hughes from Clanfield in East
OL,7,FHampshire is a keen gardener and
OL,8,Fcomposter.JShe says: "I was brought up
OL,9,Fwith a grandma and grandad who always
OL,10,Fgardened and grew their own and had
OL,11,Fcompost bins. My Mum and Dad would
OL,12,Fhave compost bins and I've always had
OL,13,Fcompost bins.
OL,15,F"I grew up with 'waste not want'
OL,16,Fbefore it became fashionable."
