OL,3,CCompostable packaging put to the test
OL,4,Cas cups take years to break down
OL,6,FRecently she's been cutting up
OL,7,Fcompostable bags and adding it to her
OL,8,Fmix, but the results have been varied.
OL,9,FJoanne says: "It hasn't composted down
OL,10,Fafter nine months really so you end up
OL,11,Ftaking it out and putting it back in
OL,12,Fto a fresh batch, is what I've been
OL,13,Fdoing anyway."
OL,15,FOver the next year, Anita Carey will
OL,16,Fexperimenting with compostable
OL,17,Fmaterials in home systems to see how
OL,18,Fthey perform.
