OL,3,CCompostable packaging put to the test
OL,4,Cas cups take years to break down
OL,6,FShe'll also survey home composters to
OL,7,Fsee how their experiences compare.
OL,8,FThen, next April, she'll analyse the
OL,9,Fresults in the lab.
OL,11,FThe Sustainability Centre in
OL,12,FPetersfield, which is supporting the
OL,13,Fproject, bought some compostable cups
OL,14,Ffor an event as a better alternative
OL,15,Fto single-use plastic.
OL,17,FBut after five years, chief executive,
OL,18,FChristine Seaward, says the cups don't
OL,19,Fappear to be showing any signs of
OL,20,Fbreaking down.
