OL,3,CCompostable packaging put to the test
OL,4,Cas cups take years to break down
OL,6,F"Yeah, really completely surprised. I
OL,7,Fexpected it to be I don't know,
OL,8,Flooking as if it was five years old,
OL,9,Flooking as if it was degrading in some
OL,10,Fway and perhaps even breaking up. But
OL,11,Fit looks as if it's just come out of
OL,12,Fthe packet."JChristine says what's
OL,13,Fimportant is that we ask better
OL,14,Fquestions and expect better answers.
OL,15,FIt's hoped that through this project,
OL,16,Fwe might just get that.
